## Quick Start

```bash
# Install dependencies
go mod tidy

# Run locally
go run ./cmd/main.go

# Build
go build -o bin/{{.Name}} ./cmd/main.go{{if .WithDocker}}

# Run with Docker
docker compose up{{end}}
```

