## Development

```bash
# Run unit tests
go test ./...

# Run integration tests (requires Docker)
go test -tags=integration ./...

# Skip integration tests in a quick pass
go test -short ./...

# Lint
golangci-lint run{{if .WithDocker}}

# Docker build
docker build -t {{.Name}} .{{end}}
```

{{if .WithCI}}CI/CD workflow files are included for the selected provider.{{end}}
Integration tests use testcontainers to provision PostgreSQL automatically.

